l%20search%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Alphabet%20CEO%20testified%20in%20an%20antitrust%20case%20that%20could%20force%20Google%20to%20sell%20Chrome%20and%20share%20data.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPichai%20also%20played%20up%20the%20competition%20Google%20faces%20from%20AI%20chatbots%20like%20OpenAI's%20Chat%20GPT.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-alphabet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAlphabet%3C%2Fa%3E%20CEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%20said%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20concerns%20around%20privacy%26quot%3B%20if%20Google%20is%20forced%20to%20sell%20some%20of%20the%20data%20it%20collects%20to%20create%20its%20search%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-case-chrome-android-sale-monopoly-doj-remedy-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20are%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20three-week%20court%20battle%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20that%20could%20result%20in%20a%20massive%20shake-up%20of%20the%20%241.8%20trillion%20tech%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPichai%20testified%20in%20Google's%20monopoly%20case%20on%20Wednesday.%20US%20District%20Judge%20Amit%20Mehta%20ruled%20in%20August%20that%20Google's%20online%20search%20business%20violated%20US%20antitrust%20law%20and%20will%20ultimately%20determine%20Google's%20fate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20remedies%20the%20Justice%20Department%20is%20seeking%20would%20require%20Google%20to%20sell%20its%20Chrome%20browser%20and%20share%20some%20of%20the%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20how%20the%20government's%20proposed%20remedy%20would%20affect%20Google's%20business%2C%20Pichai%20warned%20about%20the%20impact%20on%20people's%20search%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20search%20in%20Google%20in%20their%20most%20vulnerable%20moments%2C%20and%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20no%20privacy%20protections%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20cal