er%20and%20CEO.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66603e74cc442a2f676e0d23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMillennium%20founder%20Izzy%20Englander%20was%20able%20to%20lure%20one%20of%20Balyasny's%20top%20stockpickers.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20McMullan%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Jenny%20Chang-Rodriguez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBalyasny%20executive%20Steve%20Schurr%20was%20poached%20by%20Millennium%20for%20a%20pay%20package%20of%20%24100%20million.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESchurr%2C%20a%20journalist%20and%20short-seller%20before%20joining%20Balyasny%2C%20was%20one%20of%20the%20firm's%20top%20stockpickers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESchurr's%20presentation%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Alabama%20in%20March%20outlined%20his%20investment%20process.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20eye-popping%20headline%20in%20the%20hedge%20fund%20industry's%20talent%20war%20is%20Steve%20Schurr's%20move%20from%20Balyasny%20to%20Millennium%20and%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-04-29%2Fmillennium-poaches-balyasny-s-schurr-with-100-million-offer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%24100%20million%20pay%20package%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20took%20to%20poach%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESchurr%2C%20a%20former%20financial%20journalist%20at%20the%20Financial%20Times%20and%20short-seller%20who%20worked%20with%20legendary%20investor%20Jim%20Chanos%2C%20was%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20equities%20rebuild%20that%20%2423%20billion%20Balyasny%20has%20undergone.%20He%20worked%20alongside%20the%20firm's%20founder%20and%20executives%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbalyasny-trims-asia-equity-head-archana-parekh-book-lead-buildout-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArchana%20Parekh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20head%20of%20Asian%20equities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdmitry-balyasny-interview-rebuild-hedge-fund-equities-unit-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20the%20end%20of%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20firm's%20thinking%20about%20equities%20investing%2C%20Schurr%20said%20Balyasny%20tapped%20him%20to%20build%20a%20centralized%20research%20function%20for%20stockpicking%20teams%20that%20focused%20on%20primary%20research%20in%20addition%20to%20managing%20a%20large%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20he'll%20be%20taking%20his%20talents%20to%20Izzy%20Englander's%20%2473%20billion%20manager%20after%20he%20sits%20out%20a%20year%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20non-compete%20clause%20in%20his%20contract.%20His%20pay%20package%20includes%20incentives%20that%20will%20take%20years%20to%20pay%20out%2C%20%3Cspan%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-hedge-fund-career-multistrategy-portfolio-manager-churn-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultistrategy%20portfolio%20managers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Schurr%20didn't%20want%20to%20use%20alternative%20data%20like%20credit-card%20receipts%20to%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Btriangulating%20and%20calling%20quarters%26quot%3B%20by%20estimating%20a%20company's%20earnings%20before%20they're%20released%2C%20calling%20the%20popular%20investing%20process%20%26quot%3Ba%20strategy%20of%20diminished%20expected%20returns%26quot%3B%20when%20he%20spoke%20to%20BI%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20presentation%20at%20a%20conference%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Alabama's%20Culverhouse%20College%20of%20Business%20this%20March%2C%20Schurr%20went%20into%20greater%20detail%20about%20how%20he%20finds%20opportunities%20and%20researches%20potential%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22350499e4-99e4-412c-926e-22c5f87cbd7a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20past%20the%20narrative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recording%20of%20his%20presentation%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20Schurr%20described%20how%20he%20applies%20a%20short-seller's%20lens%20to%20long%20bets%20in%20his%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20turn%20a%20situation%20upside%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20%26quot%3BWall%20Street%20is%20a%20perpetual%20optimism%20machine%26quot%3B%20that%20forces%20investors%20to%20dig%20deep%20to%20find%20the%20real%20valuation%20of%20a%20stock%2C%20not%20just%20the%20%26quot%3Bnarrative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20used%20his%20experience%20as%20a%20short-seller%20to%20identify%20three%20buckets%20of%20stocks%20with%20%26quot%3Bcertain%20types%20of%20things%20we%20should%20never%20short.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20buckets%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECompounders%2C%20such%20as%20Nvidia%2C%20Tesla%2C%20and%20one%20of%20his%20holdings%2C%20Reddit.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECompanies%20with%20a%20competitive%20moat%2C%20such%20as%20holdings%20of%20his%20like%20Brink's%20and%20Walmart-connected%20gas%20station%20chain%20Murphy%20USA.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBad%20businesses%20with%20a%20recent%20positive%20change%2C%20such%20as%20Abercrombie%20%26amp%3B%20Fitch%2C%20which%20has%20had%20a%20multi-year%20turnaround%20under%20a%20new%20CEO.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20of%20the%20research%20process%20as%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20work%20I%20did%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20not%20a%20secret%20trove%20of%20information%20that%20no%20one%20else%20has%20access.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20thing%20you%20can%20do%20is%20doing%20the%20research%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20recommending%20industry%20conferences%20and%20expert%20networks%20over%20sell-side-organized%20events%20and%20meetings%20with%20company%20executives%20and%20investor%20relations%20teams.%20He%20recommended%20data%20providers%20such%20as%20280first%2C%20Zion%20Research%2C%20and%20BamSEC%20to%20augment%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWall%20Street%20is%20an%20echo%20chamber%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20good%20investors%20look%20outside%20of%20the%20normal%20channels.%20He%20pointed%20to%20YouTube%20reviews%20of%20consumer%20products%20and%20Reddit%20forums%20dedicated%20to%20a%20specific%20company%20as%20places%20where%20investors%20could%20glean%20insights%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20slide%20titled%20%26quot%3BHow%20We%20Maintain%20Performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Schurr%20outlined%20that%20his%20teams%20%26quot%3Bthrive%20in%20obscurity%26quot%3B%20and%20look%20for%20stocks%20with%20less%20than%20three%20teams%20covering%20the%20name.%20Companies%20with%20market%20caps%20between%20%241%20billion%20and%20%245%20billion%20market%20cap%20have%20been%20a%20sweet%20spot%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20duration%20is%20also%20critical.%20The%20ability%20to%20hold%20a%20stock%20through%20volatile%20markets%20is%20important%2C%20Schurr%20said%2C%20telling%20the%20students%20in%20attendance%20that%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20money%20to%20be%20made%26quot%3B%20is%20going%20to%20come%20from%20yearslong%20positions%2C%20not%20quarterly%20wins.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20market%20is%20going%20to%20change%20constantly%20over%20the%20next%2020%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20tools%20like%20alternative%20data%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20are%20%26quot%3Bcommoditized%20very%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20durable%20is%20deep%20fundamental%20equity%20research%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-schurr-investing-style-millennium-balyasny-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746024149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68123306a466d2b74ab4908d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-schurr-investi