Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20made%20a%20firm%20commitment%20to%20avoiding%20the%20most%20common%20mistakes%20that%20land%20couples%20in%20my%20office.%20Here%20are%20the%20ways%20that%20you%20can%20avoid%20them%2C%20too%2C%20and%20keep%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-of-strong-marriage-couples-therapist-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarriage%20healthy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b0ad780-f01c-400e-8b8c-629c8beebcb3%5C%22%3EDon't%20prioritize%20work%20(or%20kids)%20over%20your%20marriage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20absolutely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-prioritized-career-over-personal-life-have-almost-no-regrets-2019-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecannot%20prioritize%20your%20career%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20your%20marriage.%20This%20is%20true%20for%20men%20and%20women.%20One%20of%20my%20clients%20was%20a%20touring%20musician%20who%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20away%20from%20home.%20He%20was%20surprised%20when%20his%20wife%20filed%20for%20divorce%2C%20but%20I%20wasn't.%20He%20might%20have%20thought%20he%20was%20there%20for%20her%2C%20but%20his%20actions%20showed%20he%20was%20choosing%20his%20career%20over%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20can%20be%20said%20for%20kids.%20Of%20course%20you%20love%20your%20children%20and%20need%20to%20look%20after%20their%20physical%20and%20emotional%20needs%2C%20but%20don't%20forget%20your%20spouse.%20My%20nephew%20has%20young%20children%20and%20I%20regularly%20watch%20his%20kids%20so%20he%20can%20have%20one-on-one%20time%20with%20his%20wife.%20That's%20so%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ff6fcb4-7718-42a8-98f6-620291d73ac9%5C%22%3EDon't%20fall%20into%20social%20media%20temptation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20reconnecting%20with%20old%20flames%20to%20secret%20messages%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-divorce-playbook-changed-messy-sophie-turner-joe-jonas-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20is%20fueling%20modern%20divorces%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20soon%20as%20you%20start%20checking%20in%20on%20the%20profile%20of%20an%20old%20boyfriend%20or%20girlfriend%2C%20you've%20crossed%20a%20line.%20Now%2C%20instead%20of%20thinking%20about%20your%20spouse%2C%20you're%20thinking%20about%20this%20old%20love.%20This%20plants%20a%20seed%20where%20suddenly%20you're%20considering%20other%20options%20and%20what%20life%20might%20look%20like%20with%20someone%20other%20than%20your%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20makes%20us%20think%20that%20the%20grass%20may%20be%20greener%20somewhere%20else.%20But%20as%20a%20married%20person%2C%20you%20should%20be%20thinking%20about%20your%20own%20home%20%E2%80%94%20watering%20and%20fertilizing%20your%20own%20lawn%20to%20make%20it%20beautiful%20alongside%20your%20spouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e27768a3-b4ee-404c-b773-425df7c3d4da%5C%22%3EDon't%20just%20communicate%2C%20comprehend%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20was%20an%20attorney%2C%20I%20was%20a%20communications%20major.%20In%20both%20roles%2C%20I%20saw%20that%20people%20often%20talk%20without%20actually%20listening%20to%20what%20the%20other%20person%20is%20saying.%20This%20can%20happen%20in%20innocent%20ways%2C%20like%20when%20we%20rush%20to%20finish%20our%20spouse's%20sentence%20because%20we%20know%20what%20they're%20going%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20frustration%20and%20resentment.%20Try%20to%20pause%20and%20be%20present%20in%20conversations.%20Don't%20make%20assumptions.%20Ask%20your%20spouse%20questions%20to%20know%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can't%20do%20this%20in%20every%20conversation%2C%20but%20if%20you%20make%20time%20to%20do%20it%20each%20week%2C%20you%20might%20notice%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20your%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228862f5c8-a374-4d07-8630-3bf01312beba%5C%22%3EDon't%20rush%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20know%20that%20old%20say