ssenger's%20device%20got%20stuck%20in%20a%20seat%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflew-on-hawaiian-airlines-new-york-honolulu-review-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHawaiian%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20Flight%20457%20was%20traveling%20from%20Honolulu%20to%20Tokyo%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPartway%20through%20the%20journey%2C%20flight%20attendants%20noticed%20an%20%26quot%3Belectrical%20smell%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20cabin%2C%20an%20airline%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bcoming%20from%20a%20guest's%20mobile%20device%20that%20became%20lodged%20in%20a%20seat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pilots%20then%20declared%20an%20emergency%2C%20which%20allowed%20them%20to%20obtain%20priority%20handling%20at%20Tokyo's%20Haneda%20Airport.%20This%20was%20done%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20an%20abundance%20of%20caution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20the%20airline's%20team%20was%20able%20to%20remove%20the%20device%20from%20the%20seat%20after%20everyone%20deplaned%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSafety%20is%20our%20priority%2C%20and%20we%20apologize%20to%20impacted%20guests%20for%20the%20inconvenience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirlines%20take%20trapped%20devices%20very%20seriously%20because%20lithium%20batteries%20can%20catch%20fire%20and%20spread%20throughout%20the%20cabin%2C%20creating%20a%20potentially%20dangerous%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirlines%20tell%20passengers%20to%20keep%20devices%20in%20the%20cabin%20rather%20than%20the%20hold%20so%20that%20any%20problems%20can%20be%20spotted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Japanese%20news%20outlets%20reported%20that%20the%20device%20caught%20fire%2C%20but%20the%20airline%20told%20BI%20this%20wasn't%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20January%2C%20an%20Air%20Busan%20Airbus%20A321%20caught%20fire%20shortly%20before%20takeoff%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20inju