9-1745848510.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-9-1745848510-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-9-1745848510-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-9-1745848510-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fpalaash-farm-to-table-dining-9-1745848510-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-423647%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmninder%20Sandhu%20is%20the%20creative%20force%20behind%20Palaash%2C%20a%20wildlife%20dining%20experience%20near%20Nagpur%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20nostalgia%20is%20a%20by-product%20of%20her%20cooking%3B%20her%20culinary%20techniques%20come%20laced%20with%20a%20fondness%20for%20those%20times.%20Even%20as%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%98slow%20cooking%E2%80%99%20kicked%20into%20the%20common%20parlance%20recently%20after%20a%20hiatus%20that%20lasted%20decades%2C%20for%20chef%20Amninder%2C%20it%20was%20something%20she%E2%80%99d%20been%20championing%20routinely.%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20a%20%3Cem%3Esardarni%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20Sikh%20woman)%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20the%20Northeast.%20For%20me%2C%20bamboo%20smoked%20pork%20is%20just%20as%20important%20as%20an%20%3Cem%3Ealoo%20paratha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20gas-free%20style%20of%20cooking%20that%20her%20food%20exemplifies%2C%20she%20credits%20interactions%20with%20the%20granddaughter%20of%20Maharaja%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20of%20Patiala.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20at%20the%20Taj%2C%20she%20shared%20some%20of%20her%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F308289%2Ffood-writers-compile-a-kitchen-o